summary: Retexture of Omegared99's battlemage with Amidianborn's textures.
descriptionHtml:
Retexture of Omegared99's battlemage with Amidianborn's textures. White version is ready by now. Working on the other colors.
Original mod had 1k textures, I changed those to AMB's high res textures. 2k-4k
Original can be found here, pls endorse.
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10277/?
Credits to Omegared99 and Amidianborn.
I just put this together and fixed/activated the environmentmapping.
